nodes.text: "Brother" Fivelines was a droid that inhabited Ronyards. He met C-3PO and R2-D2 while they were on a mission for Rebel Alliance. When the Empire invaded Ronyards in order to start mining Varium, he tried to convince a group of stormtroopers to leave, but they destroyed him. However, his "death" caused Ronyards to rebel against the invaders and kill them.
